# AGV Data Source Plugin

## Project Files
- AgvDataSource.java      # Main source code
- agv-config.properties   # Configuration file
- compile_and_deploy.bat  # Build script
- AGV数据采集插件说明文档.md  # Documentation

## IDE & Build
- *.class
- *.jar
- *.bat (except compile_and_deploy.bat)
- .idea/
- *.iml

## OS
- Thumbs.db
- .DS_Store
- Desktop.ini

## Misc
- .gitconfig
- .npmrc
- config.yaml
- .zshrc
- .python_history
